MASTERS TOURNAMENT
April 5, 2007
K.J. Choi
START_OF_INTERVIEW_TEXT







 Q.  On the course conditions? 
 K. J. CHOI:  Today's wind direction is very difficult.  Greens are hard.  More harder greens because of no rain. 
 The wind keeps changing.  That made it more difficult than the practice round. 
 If the weather stays dry, it will play harder and firmer. 



END_OF_INTERVIEW_TEXT